vernitron <vrn> sets record date for merger vote
    deer park, n.y., june 29 - 
vernitron corp said it has set a new record date for shareholders
entitled to vote on the proposed merger of vernitron corp with sb
holding corp for july 10. vernitron, which manufactures
electromechanical components and related products and services, said
it expects that a special meeting of shareholders will be held in
august. vernitron said that sb holding holds 55.2 pct in vernitron,
resulting from a tender offer in november 1986. reuter 
